512
01:14:23,391 --> 01:14:26,519
The quarterback?
- Yes ma'am.

513
01:14:26,686 --> 01:14:32,610
Father Michael and I, we listen
to all the games on the Hi-Fi.

514
01:14:32,777 --> 01:14:36,739
I'm Sister Dolores. Please come in.

515
01:14:39,951 --> 01:14:43,580
I'm sorry sister, I know it's late.
