- Oh, I ask the Lord that every day.

542
01:17:13,124 --> 01:17:18,755
Doctors blamed genetics but I don't
know. She was small...

543
01:17:18,922 --> 01:17:22,217
and weaker than
the other children.

544
01:17:22,384 --> 01:17:27,140
But I had faith that
God would protect her.

545
01:17:30,852 --> 01:17:36,650
Angela believed in her own
kind of protection.

546
01:17:38,277 --> 01:17:43,283
An angel?
- Faith is all-powerful.

547
01:17:43,450 --> 01:17:49,540
If one truly believes in something,
one will make it come true.

548
01:17:51,417 --> 01:17:57,424
Of course, we have to be careful
what we choose to believe in.

549
01:17:58,133 --> 01:18:03,055
Duty calls. Forgive me.
I'll be right back.

550
01:18:13,192 --> 01:18:17,738
Hey, you play any football?
