What are you doing?

559
01:19:56,683 --> 01:20:00,396
Did you know about these?
- What are they?

560
01:20:00,563 --> 01:20:03,232
Why would she draw these?

561
01:20:04,734 --> 01:20:07,570
Those can't be Angela's.

562
01:20:19,876 --> 01:20:21,836
Just in case.

563
01:20:28,219 --> 01:20:29,929
Hey kid, is that you?

564
01:20:33,058 --> 01:20:37,104
What is this thing?
- I don't know.

565
01:20:38,688 --> 01:20:40,358
Whatever it is...

566
01:20:42,110 --> 01:20:43,820
it's real.

567
01:22:41,661 --> 01:22:44,163
What in God's name?

568
01:22:48,585 --> 01:22:50,462
Who are you?

569
01:22:57,595 --> 01:23:01,350
He's gone.

570
01:23:03,394 --> 01:23:09,067
What happened? Are you okay?
- It's too late. It's too late.

571
01:23:10,193 --> 01:23:13,280
Look at this.
- I don't understand. What's going on?

572
01:23:13,447 --> 01:23:17,285
It is the ghost.
- Ghost? What ghost?

573
01:23:17,452 --> 01:23:20,746
From the game.
- Who are you?

574
01:23:20,913 --> 01:23:24,710
You're not Angela's friend.
What do you want from her?

575
01:23:24,877 --> 01:23:28,046
She's suffered enough.
- You get out of here.

576
01:23:28,213 --> 01:23:31,842
Leave the poor girl in peace.
- God sees you, Ms. Channing.

577
01:23:32,010 --> 01:23:34,554
God sees everything.

578
01:23:42,813 --> 01:23:48,445
Who was that lady? And what the hell were you doing
out here in the middle of the freaking night?

579
01:23:49,529 --> 01:23:53,784
It doesn't matter anymore.
They're all gone, it's over.

580
01:23:53,950 --> 01:23:58,122
Sandy, nobody knows where you've been.

581
