If you're in some kind of trouble,
you can talk to me.

582
01:24:04,213 --> 01:24:09,092
It doesn't matter anymore, Eli. It doesn't matter.
- Stop saying that.

583
01:24:13,890 --> 01:24:16,684
It matters to me.

584
